'''Belz Crater''' is an [[impact crater]] in the [[Oxia Palus quadrangle]] of [[Mars]], located at 23.93° N and 43.23° W.  It is 10.21&nbsp;km in diameter and was named after the city of [[Belz]], [[Lviv Oblast]], [[Ukraine]].<ref>{{gpn|683}}</ref>

