'''''Under det rosa täcket''''' (English: ''Under the Pink Duvet'') is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[feminism|feminist]] book written by [[Nina Björk]], first published in 1996. The book made a great impact on the Swedish feminist field of the 1990s and is notable for introducing [[Judith Butler|Butlerian]] [[queer theory]] to Sweden.{{Fact|date=June 2017}}

